Peru to Boost Andean Bourse Integration, Castilla Says

-- B y   J o h n   Q u i g l e y
-- 
2011-09-21T14:41:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/peru-to-boost-andean-bourse-integration-castilla-says.html
Peruvian Finance Minister Miguel
Castilla said the government will seek to push forward the
integration of its stock market with those of Chile and
 Colombia .  Peru stands to gain most from the bourse integration
project, known as Mila, Castilla told investors at an event in
the Princeton Club of  New York  today.  “I think the Mila is an excellent initiative that should
be pursued,” he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
John Quigley in Lima at 
 jquigley8@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Philip Sanders at 
 psanders@bloomberg.net  